         </div>
         <div type="edition" ana="#b1" xml:lang="grc" subtype="transcription" xml:id="elus0066.transcription" corresp="#elus0066.diplomatic #elus0066.translation">
            <p>
               <supplied reason="lost">τοῦ Κυρίου ἡ γῆ κα</supplied>ὶ τὸ πλήρ<supplied reason="lost">ωμα αὐτῆς</supplied>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" ana="#b1" xml:id="elus0066.translation" corresp="#elus0066.diplomatic #elus0066.transcription">
            <p>The earth is the Lord's and the fullness thereof</p>
