      <back>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>Tombstone has circular head and shaft. The head of the stone is mostly lost. Only a portion of the transcription of the tombstone survives. A possible transcription and translation were constructed. The letters of the inscription are sharply cut. The inscription is from Psalms 24:1.</p>
         </div>
